    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Window shutters having a vertical folding blade system in a frame, designed to cover a large expanse quickly. An example of such shutters is for hurricane protection. For window coverings with lighter weight vertical slats attached only at the top, use "vertical blinds."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
